Package com.jackychu.app.tictactoe

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ErrorMessage
    The class for http response to represent error message.
    Game
    This class store the tic-tac-toe (3x3) game status.
    Each cell on the board is one of three kind of values: 0 for no mark, 1 for player 1, 2 for player 2.
    Players who is O or X depends on UI representation
    TODO: Enhance to support dimension larger than 3
    GameResource
    Game resource (exposed at "/api/v1.0/game" path)
    Main
    System start point class
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Game.Status
    The status of game.
